    "7879692": {
      "title": "Bursting strength evaluation after different types of mesh fixation in laparoscopic herniorrhaphy",
      "abstract": "Background: In laparoscopic inguinal herniorrhaphy, meshes commonly have been fixed with a stapler. Recently, a new mode of fixation using a helical fastener has been introduced. The purpose of this experimental study was to compare the stability achieved by various types of mesh fixation."
